00:46:12,560 --> 00:46:14,520
Go change! Quickly! We’re late.

539
00:46:15,960 --> 00:46:16,960
Really?
Really.

540
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,440
What’s the color?
Pink.

541
00:46:20,840 --> 00:46:23,160
Oliang!

542
00:46:30,360 --> 00:46:31,680
Okay?
Okay.

543
00:46:31,920 --> 00:46:34,320
I’ve got something to tell you.

544
00:46:34,320 --> 00:46:38,880
I’m wearing pink today,
and I think I met my soulmate down by the entrance of your condo.

545
00:46:39,160 --> 00:46:43,000
I wonder which floor he is on and what room number.

546
00:46:43,480 --> 00:46:46,360
I really have to come here more often.

547
00:46:48,160 --> 00:46:50,720
I am the most handsome one here.

548
00:46:52,280 --> 00:46:52,920
Right.

549
00:46:59,160 --> 00:47:01,560
Oh, I’m sorry.
That’s okay.

550
00:47:05,120 --> 00:47:06,800
Wait a second. I forgot my bag.

551
00:47:11,360 --> 00:47:12,520
Sorry.

552
00:47:12,680 --> 00:47:15,080
Which way are you going?

553
00:47:16,280 --> 00:47:16,920
Oh!

554
00:47:17,280 --> 00:47:18,360
I’m sorry.

555
00:47:18,440 --> 00:47:19,480
You all right?

556
00:47:19,600 --> 00:47:20,880
Yes, hello!

557
00:47:21,720 --> 00:47:22,800
Oh, okay.

558
00:47:23,760 --> 00:47:25,080
Yes, yes, for sure.

559
00:47:25,920 --> 00:47:26,840
Oliang!

560
00:47:28,760 --> 00:47:29,720
Don’t go outside.

561
00:47:32,240 --> 00:47:33,080
Thank you.

562
00:47:33,320 --> 00:47:34,720
There’s still something on the floor.

563
00:47:34,840 --> 00:47:35,960
Oh, thanks.

564
00:47:37,520 --> 00:47:38,640
Be good.

565
00:47:42,800 --> 00:47:44,480
I almost missed it. Thank you.

566
00:47:53,360 --> 00:47:54,760
Young man…

567
00:47:55,560 --> 00:47:57,080
young man, you forgot something.

568
00:47:57,080 --> 00:47:57,960
Thank you.

569
00:48:08,560 --> 00:48:10,360
Phu!

570
00:48:15,160 --> 00:48:16,520
Nan!

571
00:48:41,320 --> 00:48:45,080
I used to think that sharing my thoughts like this would help,

572
00:48:45,840 --> 00:48:49,920
but it just reminds me that you’re not here in my life.

573
00:48:52,240 --> 00:48:58,280
I’m not going to forget you. You’ll always be my best friend, Phu.

574
00:48:58,960 --> 00:48:59,880
Phu

575
00:49:16,360 --> 00:49:20,640
Jo, I simply must have that room.

576
00:49:24,520 --> 00:49:26,240
It just can’t be any other room.
